OL,4,G0000FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GCraig and his crew log a burned
OL,6,     Gforest north of Kamloops, but the
OL,7,     Glethal mix of ash and rain takes
OL,8,     Ga toll on the machines and crew.
OL,9,     GBrent clears a fire guard around
OL,10,     Ga homestead.
OL,11,G0100FOutback Truckers
